    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "Inland\nAIR LInEs\nEffective November 1, 1939\nMT. RUSHMORE*\nServing America's Vacationland",
      "Inland\nAIR LInES\nSAFETY FIRST\nIS INLAND'S\nMAXIM.\nTWO VETERAN\nPILOTS ARE ON\nEVERY FLIGHT\nTravel over Inland Skylanes\nhas increased 118% in the past\nyear. This popularity shows\nthat more and more exper-\nienced travelers appreciate\nthe Safety, Speed, and Com-\nfort of Flying with INLAND.\nTake to the Inland Skylanes\nfor a safe, swift, scenic jour-\nney over the West's most his-\ntoric frontiers. You will feel\nrelaxed, secure, in the restful\ncabins of Inland's powerful,\ntwin-motored Boeing planes.\nThat comfort and security\ncomes from the careful atten-\ntion to all important details\non all Inland flights.\nIT PAYS TO -\nFLY"
